# Quiz Application in C++

A simple **console-based Quiz Application** built using **C++ and DSA concepts**.  
This project demonstrates:
- Use of arrays, structures, and loops
- Input/output handling in C++
- Score calculation and display
- Clean modular code

---

## Features
✅ Multiple-choice questions  
✅ Automatic score calculation  
✅ User-friendly menu system  
✅ Easily extendable (add more questions)

---

## How to Run
1. Clone this repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/<your-username>/Quiz-Application.git
   cd Quiz-Application/src
   ```
2. Compile the code:
   ```bash
   g++ quiz.cpp -o quiz
   ```
3. Run the application:
   ```bash
   ./quiz
   ```

---

